frames.caption: A colossal statue of Anubis stands amidst an ancient Egyptian setting, towering over a procession of people. The scene is set in a desert landscape with pyramids and stone structures, evoking a sense of historical grandeur.
frames.description: The image depicts a majestic and imposing statue of Anubis, the ancient Egyptian deity, in a desert environment. A large group of people, dressed in traditional garments, are walking towards the statue, suggesting a ritual or ceremonial procession.

frames.caption: A towering figure with the head of a jackal stands amidst ancient ruins, holding ropes attached to a group of people. The scene is set in a dusty, desert-like environment with pyramids and stone structures in the background.
frames.description: The image depicts an imposing, mythical figure resembling Anubis, the Egyptian god, in a historical setting. The figure is surrounded by a group of people who appear to be laborers or slaves, suggesting a scene from ancient Egypt.
